  <brief_title>Video Assisted Ablation of Pilonidal Sinus</brief_title>
  <official_title>Video Assisted Ablation of Pilonidal Sinus. Evaluation of Safety and Efficacy of a New Minimally Invasive Technique</official_title>
  <sponsors>
